---
title: German-Style Smoky Chicken Penne  with Dark Meat Chicken, Broccoli & Lemon
description: Smoky, tangy, and creamy are the hallmarks of this delicious and quick (20-minute!) pasta. You’ll toss sautéed dark meat chicken and zucchini with al dente penne in a tangy lemon cream sauce swirled with smoky mustard. Finish with a squeeze of fresh lemon juice and shower of fresh green chives, and dig right in!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66fc209d44b7013be522e822-5aae007f.jpeg
